title: Winter Concert
desc:
The  winter concert  directed by music teacher Remy Loumbrozo will take place in the auditorium on? Tuesday, December 15, 2015 from 6pm to 8pm . Like every year, the concert will comprehend music performances from the primary and secondary students as well as LFNY staff.  
 The event is free.  Tickets are limited to 5 per family . Reservation is compulsory.  There is no ticket. ?On the day of, your name will be on the list and the seating will be on a first come first serve basis. 
  If you decide  not to attend please let us know 2 days in advance  so we can give the seats to other parents on the waiting list.
